Joshua Kealiher wrote:

> Last night I just got my '62 EZ Camper!!! I can't wait to dive in. I do need
> some constructive advice on getting the surface rust taken care of.

I cut down the surface rust on my '65 Single Cab with scotch brite pads and
final sand (baby poop looking sanding compound). After all was said and done I
polished the whole thing out and have been happy with it ever since.

